    {
      "id": "ft_44_f3tku4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 898,
      "width": 1938.2399999999998,
      "height": 65,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 476258345,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 559207953,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782572274154,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "• Critical gap: entire pre-spawn agent guard chain (agent-model-guard, no-haiku-enforcer, maestro-enforcer) is registered under matcher 'Agent' while the live subagent tool emits 'Task' — zero pre-spawn enforcement on every subagent call (D2b-01, D10c-02).\n• Dashed edge codegraph→Context Bus: proposed_bus_updates computed on every codegraph call but SubagentStop has 0 registrations across repo/active/template — the bus symbol layer (focus_symbols, recent_findings) has no writers (D1A-001, D10c-01).\n• Memory reads bus for recall bias (biasByFocus) but focus_symbols is always empty — the bias is a no-op until ST-01 (SubagentStop wire) lands.\n• PageIndex pillar: per-prompt hook disabled 2026-06-01 after 0/16 query-hits at up to 15.8s/prompt — listed as a Six Pillar but effectively on-demand only.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• Critical gap: entire pre-spawn agent guard chain (agent-model-guard, no-haiku-enforcer, maestro-enforcer) is registered under matcher 'Agent' while the live subagent tool emits 'Task' — zero pre-spawn enforcement on every subagent call (D2b-01, D10c-02).\n• Dashed edge codegraph→Context Bus: proposed_bus_updates computed on every codegraph call but SubagentStop has 0 registrations across repo/active/template — the bus symbol layer (focus_symbols, recent_findings) has no writers (D1A-001, D10c-01).\n• Memory reads bus for recall bias (biasByFocus) but focus_symbols is always empty — the bias is a no-op until ST-01 (SubagentStop wire) lands.\n• PageIndex pillar: per-prompt hook disabled 2026-06-01 after 0/16 query-hits at up to 15.8s/prompt — listed as a Six Pillar but effectively on-demand only.",
